Sign Up (Single Screen, multi-step)

Step 1: Email + Password
  └── Step 2: First + Last Name
        └── Step 3: Role Selection [1]
              │
              ├── "Customer"
              │     └── Step 4a: Add Vehicle (Year, Make, Model, VIN) [1]
              │           └── → (tabs)/search
              │
              └── "Service Provider"
                    └── Step 4b: Provider Type [1]
                          ├── Detailer
                          └── Mechanic
                                └── Step 5: Select Services from catalog
                                      └── Step 6: Bio + Mile Radius
                                            └── → (auth)/pending-approval


Sign In

sign-in.tsx
  ├── Email + Password  →  supabase.auth.signInWithPassword()
  ├── Google / Facebook →  supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth() [1]
  │     └── First OAuth login? → check if users row exists
  │           ├── YES → continue
  │           └── NO  → go to Step 2 of sign-up
  │
  └── On success: read users.is_provider
        ├── FALSE             → (tabs)/search
        ├── TRUE + approved   → (tabs)/more/provider
        └── TRUE + pending    → (auth)/pending-approval


Forgot Password

forgot-password.tsx
  └── supabase.auth.resetPasswordForEmail()
        └── Supabase sends email link → back to sign-in


Mutation Order on Final Submit

1. supabase.auth.signUp()         → creates auth.users row
2. trigger fires                  → creates public.users row
3. UPDATE users                   → first_name, last_name, is_provider
4a. (Customer)  INSERT user_car_information
4b. (Provider)  INSERT providers (is_approved = FALSE)
5.  (Provider)  INSERT provider_services for each selected catalog item


Session Handling

onAuthStateChange()
  ├── SIGNED_IN      → fetch users row → hydrate state
  ├── SIGNED_OUT     → clear state → (auth)/sign-in
  └── TOKEN_REFRESHED → update session silently


Components Involved (src/components/auth/) 

    StepIndicator.tsx — progress through sign-up steps
    RoleSelector.tsx — customer vs provider UI
    ServicePicker.tsx — catalog services filtered by provider type
    VehicleForm.tsx — customer vehicle fields
